response.original_title: SPACE SHOWER SWEET LOVE SHOWER 2025 30th ANNIVERSARY -DAY1-
response.overview: Space Shower's summer festival "SWEET LOVE SHOWER" is back again this year! This year marks the festival's 30th anniversary, and we'll be broadcasting the three days of the festival in an extra-long program that will run for 5 hours each day, for a total of 15 hours!
